title: 1996 Indian Federation Cup
text: The 1996 Indian Federation Cup was the 21st season of the <a href="Federation%20Cup%20%28India%29">Indian Federation Cup</a>. The tournament started on 29 June 1996 to 11 August. The competition was won by <a href="East%20Bengal%20F.C.">East Bengal</a>, who defeated <a href="Dempo%20S.C.">Dempo</a> 2–1 in the final.
